OL,3,CMan who was killed in HGV crash on the
OL,4,CM6 near Gretna named by police
OL,6,FThe man who was killed in a crash on
OL,7,Fthe M6 near Gretna has been named.
OL,9,FCostica Balan, aged 63, died in a
OL,10,Fcollision on the M6 northbound close
OL,11,Fto Junction 45 on Thursday 2 October.
OL,13,FMr Balan, from Spalding in
OL,14,FLincolnshire, was Romanian and had
OL,15,Fbeen living in the UK for the past 16
OL,16,Fyears. He died at the scene.
OL,18,FIn a tribute his family said: "He was
OL,19,Fa beloved husband and father who will
OL,20,Fbe dearly missed by everyone."
